<HEADLINE>
FT  17 JAN 92 / World News in Brief: Forged cash haul
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
London police were questioning a man about Britain's biggest seizure of
counterfeit currency. Forged Dutch guilders with a face value of Pounds 20m
(Dollars 36m) were seized.
